00:33:44,810 --> 00:33:47,390
The miracle of creation, the miracle of redemption,

478
00:33:48,090 --> 00:33:49,630
the miracle of everlasting life.

479
00:33:50,770 --> 00:33:53,850
And it's ours because of what he did in Jesus Christ.

480
00:33:54,110 --> 00:33:55,810
Let us pray. Thank you so much.

